<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>
        Manage robots
    </title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mw-540 p-3">
        <h3 class="mt-4">🤖 Telepresence Robot Portal</h3>
        <h5 class="py-2">Admin dashboard</h5>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid bg-dark">
        <div class="container mw-540 px-3 py-2">
            <div class=" d-flex align-items-center">
                <img src="/photos/<%= id %>.png" class="rounded-circle me-2" alt="" width="42" height="42">
                <div class="d-flex py-2 me-auto">
                    <h6 class="my-auto text-white"><b><%= name %></b><br>🏛️ <%= inst %></h6>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex py-2">
                    <form method="GET" action="/admin-dashboard">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">❌ Cancel</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mw-540 py-3 px-4">
        <h6 class="mt-2"><b>Optional features – 🤖 <b class="text-primary"><%= robotName %></b></b></h6>

        <div class="progress mb-4">
            <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 66%" aria-valuenow="66" aria-valuemin="0"
                aria-valuemax="100"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-check form-switch">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="rearView">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="rearView">Configure rear-view camera</label>
        </div>
        <p class="pt-1 text-secondary">With the addition of a USB webcam, a picture-in-picture view of behind the robot
            will increase
            drivers' spatial awareness. However, this feature increases battery drain.</p>

        <div class="form-check form-switch mt-4">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="rearView">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="rearView">Configure physical hand-raising</label>
        </div>
        <p class="pt-1 text-secondary">A dedicated 'hand-raising' button in the driver interface can be used to
            actuate/trigger a device attached to the robot. This can draw attention to the robot more subtly than the
            driver making noise.</p>

    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>